_sText:
This map is designed for intense fair fights, no team should have any advantage since the whole structure is reversed like a mirror and all players spawn with identical equipment :
  • Desert Eagle
  • Maverick M4A1
  • Kevlar Armor With Helmet
  • HE Grenade
For The Fun Of It, 2 Flashbangs, 2 Smoke Grenades and 2 More HE Grenades Are Located On The "Top Floor" And the spawn point of this map is 48.
